Deployment instructions
	git clone git://github.com/samba/dotfiles.git ~/.dotfiles
	make -C ~/.dotfiles install

***
If you like this project, please FORK IT! (Use the 'Fork' button at the top of the project page.)
This lets us keep track of changes, and occasionally merge eachother's work. 
If you have questions, please contact 'samba' on Freenode (IRC), or send me a message on GitHub.
***


This is a repository of configuration for Linux working environments, especially:
 - BASH
 - VIM
 - GNU Screen

Various tools are also provided for convenience in /bin.

The goal is to provide configuration for a friendly, productive working environment.



